typedef long long int ll;
ll a[10][105]={{0}},f[10][105]={{0}};

{
    ll n,i,j,k,cnt,c[10]={0};
    bool flag;
    char ch;

        cin>>ch>>k;
        a[ch-'A'][k]++;
        c[ch-'A']++;
    }
    for(i=0;i<5;i++)
    {
        cnt=c[i]/10;
        for(j=0;j<105;j++)
            if(a[i][j] && a[i][j]>cnt) f[i][j]=1;
    }

    {
        flag=false;
        for(j=0;j<105;j++)
        {

            {
                cout<<j<<" ";
                flag=true;
            }
        }
        if(!flag) cout<<"Nothing Unusual";
        cout<<endl;
    }
    return 0;
}
